review_blob: More bitter than I prefer my ips. Smells hoppy. Tastes normal hoppy. Smells gooooooood
really flavorful. Carmel flavored slighly. Hint of chocholate, not overwhelming at all. Kinda like a perfect amount to make it not taste stouty.
Light, tastes a lil watered down, super small hint of hops and citrus. Tasts a lil flat anf not sharp
beer_name: Cedar Creek Lawn Ranger Cream Ale
